{
  "stem": "4760.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And sometimes we had guards behind us, because we had started it, and they [? noticed ?] what was going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So on the-- then on the end, when the rocket was being finished up, they would throw in wires, or any kind of tools, or anything, just to offset the-- because the rocket at the time was radar-controlled, though not like today.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In those days, they was-- they were still radar-controlled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we-- we would offset it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When that happened, after a while they were getting very disgusted, because we were-- we were manufacturing about 20-- 20 rockets a day, and sometimes 10, 12 would come back two-- two or three day later, because we had to do them all over again.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So in order to scare us, and to make sure that we don't do any more sabotage, when we would walk out of the tunnel, they would take 10 people at random and hang them in front of us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Or they would do it in the evening at assembly, when they were counting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They would count us almost every day, because they know people were going to run away, or something would happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then they would-- on the assembly line, they would put two big posts with another post, and then they would put 10, 12-- 10 people there with a-- with a bench underneath and a [? stool. ?] They counted one, two, three, and they would hang them, just to scare us so that we wouldn't do any more sabotage.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They know, they felt, this is the only way they could prevent people of doing things they shouldn't do, because they didn't know if you were the next, or you were the next.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You never knew who was the next to be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
